### Description of the problem
I sometimes encountered a repeating ECONNRESET error after ETIMEDOUT error. I reproduced it like the below code.
e.g.
```
for (let i = 0; i <= 10; i++) {
  try {
    res = await axios.request(config);
    break;
  } catch(e) {
    console.log(e.code);
